# ─── UnicornX Aleo — Server Environment ───
# Copy to .env before first run:  cp .env.example .env && nano .env
# systemd loads this file via EnvironmentFile=/opt/unicornxaleo/.env (see deploy/unicornx-backend.service).

# Required
NODE_ENV=production
PORT=5170
PROGRAM_ID=unicornx_v3.aleo
ADMIN_PRIVATE_KEY=<aleo_admin_private_key>
ADMIN_ADDRESS=<aleo_admin_address>
ADMIN_API_KEY=<long_random_string>

# Optional (have sensible defaults; uncomment to override)
# NETWORK=testnet
# ENDPOINT=https://api.explorer.provable.com/v1
# CONTRACT_PATH=../contracts/unicornx_v3
# LEO_PATH=leo

# Optional feature keys (heuristic fallback if unset)
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
# AI_SCORER_MODEL=google/gemma-3-4b-it:free
# TWITTERAPI_IO_KEY=
